# Rust
/target
**/*.rs.bk
# Cargo.lock is committed: this workspace ships binaries (rmap-daemon/-config),
# so a locked, reproducible dependency set is desirable.

# dvorakj-parser is an independent crate (not a workspace member); it builds
# its own target dir and, as a library, doesn't need a committed lockfile.
dvorakj-parser/target
dvorakj-parser/Cargo.lock

